  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >*This game content is purely fictional. Any resemblance is purely coincidental.</h2><br>In a distant realm, there lies a mysterious and beautiful country known as the Winter Country...<br>Currently, Winter Country is under the control of a political party called the \"Dongshan Party\"...<br>And on Winter Calendar June 4th, 1989, an event unfolded at the QianShanMen Square...<br><br>Faced with the oppression of the Dongshan Party... people finally rise up for revolution...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Utilize on-field props and mechanisms to solve puzzles!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133400/extras/8711def22b118421e74fe56ea5e14564.poster.avif?t=1756058888\" width=576 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133400/extras/8711def22b118421e74fe56ea5e14564.webm?t=1756058888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133400/extras/8711def22b118421e74fe56ea5e14564.mp4?t=1756058888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keep running, jumping! Reach the finish line!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133400/extras/f0d400fe6b809a404df955aef7d1d171.poster.avif?t=1756058888\" width=576 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133400/extras/f0d400fe6b809a404df955aef7d1d171.webm?t=1756058888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133400/extras/f0d400fe6b809a404df955aef7d1d171.mp4?t=1756058888\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
